Time Pilot v1.5____________________________________________________________________A fantastic arcade game released by Konami in 1982 and ported to the Apple IIgs by Stefan Wessels in 2024.The complete source code is available at https://github.com/StewBC/Time-PilotChanges for v1.5:- Scores are now saved and loaded when needed- If you press ESC to stop a game, you are eligible to saving your high score- External RAM sounds are now at 22kHz- The enemy explosion bug is fixed- A loader with splash screen was addedStefan Wessels &Antoine Vignau & Olivier ZardiniBrutal Deluxe Softwarebrutaldeluxe.fr